 Newly arrived Swiss fans paraded through Detroit's Metro airport, waving red 
and white flags, clanging cow bells and singing in French and German. 
</P>
<P>
 The dozens of fans, while loud, were hardly disruptive and barely drew glances 
from anyone in the terminal. JULIE CART 
