<P>
 Southern California College has hired two assistant basketball coaches, Tim 
Travers and Todd Dixon. Travers had been the head basketball coach at El Toro 
High for the last 14 years, where compiled a 175-172 record.Travers, who 
resigned his coaching job at El Toro two months ago, will continue to teach 
