<TEXT>
<P>
 Re "Can This Marriage Be Saved?" (" 'What About Me?' Asks Husband," May 30): I 
could not believe your article. Brenda is working, taking care of their child 
and responsible for cleaning, cooking, etc.And still she has to cater to Rick's 
selfishness and explain to him why she's so tired. 
</P>
<P>
 If Rick would open his eyes and look around, maybe he would see that the 
dishes are piled up, laundry needs to be done and dinner cooked. Apparently he 
is '90s enough to agree to his wife working outside the home but not enough to 
