allegedly stole a woman's purse containing more than $3,000. The second took 
place last Friday about 4 p.m. and involved a female county prosecutor who was 
jogging near Braemar Country Club. 
</P>
<P>
 Knox suggested that residents refrain from jogging or walking alone until the 
suspects are arrested. MAKI BECKER 
