into the 17,265-square-foot sixth floor of an office building at 700 N. Central 
Ave. in Glendale's central business district. 
</P>
<P>
 A savings branch operated by the thrift will also occupy 6,257 square feet of 
the eight-story building's ground floor.  
</P>
<P>
