 * Try to arrive at least two hours before a game to allow for traffic. Gates 
open three hours before the game. 
</P>
<P>
 * There will be public parking on the golf course next to the Rose Bowl. All 
parking lots will open five hours before games. Park and ride lots will open 3 
1/2 hours before games. 
</P>
