</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Capistrano Valley and La Habra high schools are among Orange County high 
schools selected as 1994 winners in the California Distinguished Schools 
program. Nearly a dozen schools in the county have received the special 
recognition for their success in instructional and curriculum reform. 
</P>
