<P>
 NBC disclaimer -- A story in Wednesday's Calendar said that there was no 
disclaimer on an NBC January special, "Treasure Island: The Adventures 
Continues," to indicate that the program was a paid advertisement for the 
Treasure Island resort in Las Vegas. But NBC officials said there was a label 
at the end of the special that noted that the show had been paid for by the 
resort's owners. 
</P>
